name: creme
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "creme" %}
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://github.com/creme-ml/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: "109e308070e023825efe0b3eb6f94898e59a24ce52da259828b2eb473dfed4c6"

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - numpy >=1.16.4
    - python >=3.6
    - scikit-learn >=0.21.2
    - scipy >=1.3.0

test:
  imports:
    - creme
    - creme.cluster
    - creme.compat
    - creme.compose
    - creme.decomposition
    - creme.ensemble
    - creme.feature_extraction
    - creme.feature_selection
    - creme.impute
    - creme.linear_model
    - creme.metrics
    - creme.multiclass
    - creme.multioutput
    - creme.naive_bayes
    - creme.optim
    - creme.optim.losses
    - creme.plot
    - creme.preprocessing
    - creme.proba
    - creme.reco
    - creme.stats
    - creme.tree
    - creme.utils

about:
  home: "https://github.com/creme-ml/creme"
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: "BSD"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "Incremental machine learning in Python"
  doc_url: "https://creme-ml.github.io"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/creme-ml/creme"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - agcopenhaver
